{"prompt": "Generate a website for a personalized tutoring service. The website should be innovative and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>LearnFlow Tutoring</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #007bff;\n            --secondary-blue: #e7f3ff;\n            --text-dark: #333333;\n            --text-light: #ffffff;\n            --accent-yellow: #ffc107;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-dark);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, #0056b3 100%);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50px;\n            left: 50%;\n            width: 300px;\n            height: 300px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-yellow);\n            color: var(--text-dark);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0a800;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--text-light);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .testimonials {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-slider {\n            display: flex;\n            overflow-x: auto;\n            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n            padding-bottom: 20px;\n            scrollbar-width: none; /* Firefox */\n            -ms-overflow-style: none;  /* IE and Edge */\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-slider::-webkit-scrollbar {\n            display: none;  /* Chrome, Safari, Opera */\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-item {\n            flex: 0 0 80%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            margin: 0 10px;\n            background-color: var(--text-light);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            scroll-snap-align: start;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-item p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-item .author {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-yellow);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Basic Responsive Adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.8em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .section h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .features-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Unlock Your Potential with LearnFlow Tutoring</h1>\n        <p>Personalized, engaging, and effective tutoring designed to help you succeed.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Why Choose LearnFlow?</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                    <h3>Expert Tutors</h3>\n                    <p>Our certified educators provide tailored guidance for your specific learning needs.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-laptop-code\"></i>\n                    <h3>Flexible Learning</h3>\n                    <p>Schedule sessions that fit your busy life, online or in-person.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Proven Results</h3>\n                    <p>Watch your grades and confidence soar with our proven teaching methods.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"testimonials\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2>What Our Students Say</h2>\n                <div class=\"testimonial-slider\">\n                    <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                        <p>\"LearnFlow completely changed how I approach my studies. The tutor was patient and explained complex topics clearly. My grades improved significantly!\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"author\">- Sarah K., High School Student</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                        <p>\"The personalized approach made all the difference. I finally understand calculus thanks to my tutor at LearnFlow. Highly recommend!\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"author\">- Michael P., College Student</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                        <p>\"As a parent, I've seen a huge boost in my child's confidence and academic performance. LearnFlow is a game-changer.\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"author\">- Emily R., Parent</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Ready to Transform Your Learning?</h2>\n            <p>Sign up for a free consultation and let us help you chart your path to success.</p>\n            <form style=\"max-width: 500px; margin: 30px auto; text-align: left;\">\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    <label for=\"name\" style=\"display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Name:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required style=\"width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    <label for=\"email\" style=\"display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Email:</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required style=\"width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    <label for=\"subject\" style=\"display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Subject:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"subject\" name=\"subject\" required style=\"width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    <label for=\"message\" style=\"display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Message:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" required style=\"width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;\"></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center;\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 LearnFlow Tutoring. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@learnflow.com\">info@learnflow.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JS for potential future enhancements like form submission handling or slider interaction\n        document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}